title: Popular Patchwork - August 2014  UK
description:
Popular Patchwork - August 2014  UK

100 Pages | True PDF | English | 24 MB 


Popular Patchwork is a practical hobby magazine for the patchwork and quilting enthusiast. With projects for everyone from the beginner to an advanced level, as well as great ideas for putting your patch-working to use. Also included with this great magazine is the latest news form the world of quilting, a community section based around show & tell, dates and details of upcoming events and activities as well as reviews for quilting design books.
